data.description: Hot Home Alert! This updated Lakewood Rambler is move in ready - Updated Kitchen, Bathrooms, LVP flooring throughout and an open floor concept that welcomes you in as soon as you open the front door. Massive Island with eating space outline the kitchen while the Master Bedroom is separated from the other two rooms - adequate privacy from other guests. The large fenced backyard is ready for your vision - just over 1/3 acre with quick access to shopping, entertainment, military bases and highways. The Villa Home is sure to impress - attached garage, utility room, covered back patio, large mature trees, and more. This lovely abode is currently fully furnished - any/all furnishings can be included in the sale. Loan is assumable!    Welcome Home
